OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early fog patches will
OL,6,Fquickly clear, then a dry day with
OL,7,Fplenty of sunshine, but some cloud
OL,8,Fbubbling up in the afternoon. Becoming
OL,9,Fvery warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with some
OL,12,Fbright or sunny spells. Risk of patchy
OL,13,Fmist and fog for northern coasts, with
OL,14,Fcloudier conditions spreading south
OL,15,Fthrough the night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA dry day with plenty of warm
OL,18,Fsunshine developing after a fairly
OL,19,Fcloudy start. Rather breezy around
OL,20,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
